message.content: cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.IR, cs.SI. The paper deals with natural language processing and machine learning techniques to rank clarification questions, which falls under the category of computational linguistics (cs.CL). The use of neural networks and expected value of perfect information also suggests a focus on artificial intelligence (cs.AI) and machine learning (cs.LG). The evaluation of the model against expert human judgments involves information retrieval (cs.IR) and the use of online resources (cs.SI).
